forge.description: Forge is a free, open-source modding API all of your favourite mods use

fabric.description: Fabric is a lightweight, experimental modding toolchain for Minecraft.

spigot.description: SpigotMC, also known simply as Spigot, is a fork of the popular Bukkit server mod. Spigot is meant to increase performance and efficiency, while maintaining compatibility with Bukkit plugins.

paper.description: Paper is the next generation of Minecraft server, compatible with Spigot plugins and offering uncompromising performance.

purpur.description: Purpur is a fork of Paper and Tuinity with the goal of providing new and interesting configuration options, which allow for creating a unique gameplay experience not seen anywhere else.

tuinity.description: Fork of Paper aimed at improving server performance at high playercounts.
